{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1372,"text":"Every day, I listen to harrowing stories\nof people fleeing for their lives,"},{"time":7545,"text":"across dangerous borders\nand unfriendly seas."},{"time":12109,"text":"But there's one story\nthat keeps me awake at night,"},{"time":16628,"text":"and it's about Doaa."}]},{"cues":[{"time":18208,"text":"A Syrian refugee, 19 years old,"},{"time":21055,"text":"she was living a grinding existence\nin Egypt working day wages."},{"time":26915,"text":"Her dad was constantly thinking\nof his thriving business back in Syria"},{"time":32326,"text":"that had been blown to pieces by a bomb."},{"time":36238,"text":"And the war that drove them there\nwas still raging in its fourth year."},{"time":42999,"text":"And the community\nthat once welcomed them there"},{"time":46232,"text":"had become weary of them."},{"time":49248,"text":"And one day, men on motorcycles\ntried to kidnap her."},{"time":53084,"text":"Once an aspiring student\nthinking only of her future,"},{"time":57857,"text":"now she was scared all the time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":62269,"text":"But she was also full of hope,"},{"time":64302,"text":"because she was in love\nwith a fellow Syrian refugee named Bassem."},{"time":69349,"text":"Bassem was also struggling in Egypt,\nand he said to Doaa,"},{"time":74383,"text":"\"Let's go to Europe; seek asylum, safety."},{"time":77773,"text":"I will work, you can study --\nthe promise of a new life.\""},{"time":82829,"text":"And he asked her father\nfor her hand in marriage."}]},{"cues":[{"time":86724,"text":"But they knew to get to Europe\nthey had to risk their lives,"},{"time":92264,"text":"traveling across the Mediterranean Sea,"},{"time":94788,"text":"putting their hands in smugglers',\nnotorious for their cruelty."},{"time":101173,"text":"And Doaa was terrified of the water."},{"time":105292,"text":"She always had been.\nShe never learned to swim."}]},{"cues":[{"time":110222,"text":"It was August that year,\nand already 2,000 people had died"},{"time":114999,"text":"trying to cross the Mediterranean,"},{"time":116977,"text":"but Doaa knew of a friend who had made it\nall the way to Northern Europe,"},{"time":120971,"text":"and she thought, \"Maybe we can, too.\""},{"time":123999,"text":"So she asked her parents if they could go,"},{"time":127025,"text":"and after a painful discussion,\nthey consented,"},{"time":130391,"text":"and Bassem paid his entire life savings --\n2,500 dollars each --"},{"time":136545,"text":"to the smugglers."}]},{"cues":[{"time":138821,"text":"It was a Saturday morning\nwhen the call came,"},{"time":142060,"text":"and they were taken by bus to a beach,\nhundreds of people on the beach."},{"time":146873,"text":"They were taken then by small boats\nonto an old fishing boat,"},{"time":150945,"text":"500 of them crammed onto that boat,"},{"time":153527,"text":"300 below, [200] above."},{"time":157466,"text":"There were Syrians, Palestinians,\nAfricans, Muslims and Christians,"},{"time":162028,"text":"100 children, including Sandra --\nlittle Sandra, six years old --"},{"time":167380,"text":"and Masa, 18 months."},{"time":171498,"text":"There were families on that boat,\ncrammed together shoulder to shoulder,"},{"time":175420,"text":"feet to feet."},{"time":176976,"text":"Doaa was sitting with her legs\ncrammed up to her chest,"},{"time":180808,"text":"Bassem holding her hand."}]},{"cues":[{"time":184386,"text":"Day two on the water,\nthey were sick with worry"},{"time":187117,"text":"and sick to their stomachs\nfrom the rough sea."}]},{"cues":[{"time":191109,"text":"Day three, Doaa had a premonition."},{"time":195068,"text":"And she said to Bassem,\n\"I fear we're not going to make it."},{"time":199645,"text":"I fear the boat is going to sink.\""},{"time":202517,"text":"And Bassem said to her,\n\"Please be patient."},{"time":205690,"text":"We will make it to Sweden,\nwe will get married"},{"time":208896,"text":"and we will have a future.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":211751,"text":"Day four, the passengers\nwere getting agitated."},{"time":215628,"text":"They asked the captain,\n\"When will we get there?\""},{"time":218788,"text":"He told them to shut up,\nand he insulted them."},{"time":222740,"text":"He said, \"In 16 hours we will reach\nthe shores of Italy.\""},{"time":226506,"text":"They were weak and weary."},{"time":229704,"text":"Soon they saw a boat approach --\na smaller boat, 10 men on board,"},{"time":233999,"text":"who started shouting at them,\nhurling insults,"},{"time":237438,"text":"throwing sticks, asking them\nto all disembark"},{"time":241812,"text":"and get on this smaller,\nmore unseaworthy boat."},{"time":245551,"text":"The parents were terrified\nfor their children,"},{"time":249093,"text":"and they collectively\nrefused to disembark."},{"time":254157,"text":"So the boat sped away in anger,"},{"time":257297,"text":"and a half an hour later, came back"},{"time":261551,"text":"and started deliberately ramming a hole\nin the side of Doaa's boat,"},{"time":267627,"text":"just below where she\nand Bassem were sitting."},{"time":271764,"text":"And she heard how they yelled,"},{"time":275127,"text":"\"Let the fish eat your flesh!\""},{"time":279599,"text":"And they started laughing\nas the boat capsized and sank."}]},{"cues":[{"time":285999,"text":"The 300 people below deck were doomed."},{"time":289757,"text":"Doaa was holding on to the side\nof the boat as it sank,"},{"time":294370,"text":"and watched in horror as a small child\nwas cut to pieces by the propeller."},{"time":302355,"text":"Bassem said to her, \"Please let go,"},{"time":304578,"text":"or you'll be swept in and the propeller\nwill kill you, too.\""},{"time":308267,"text":"And remember -- she can't swim."},{"time":310999,"text":"But she let go and she started moving\nher arms and her legs,"},{"time":315211,"text":"thinking, \"This is swimming.\""},{"time":316671,"text":"And miraculously,\nBassem found a life ring."},{"time":321806,"text":"It was one of those child's rings"},{"time":323878,"text":"that they use to play\nin swimming pools and on calm seas."},{"time":327999,"text":"And Doaa climbed onto the ring,"},{"time":330068,"text":"her arms and her legs\ndangling by the side."},{"time":334835,"text":"Bassem was a good swimmer,"},{"time":336800,"text":"so he held her hand and tread water."},{"time":342064,"text":"Around them there were corpses."},{"time":344026,"text":"Around 100 people survived initially,"},{"time":346518,"text":"and they started coming together\nin groups, praying for rescue."},{"time":351083,"text":"But when a day went by and no one came,"},{"time":355424,"text":"some people gave up hope,"},{"time":357273,"text":"and Doaa and Bassem watched"},{"time":359471,"text":"as men in the distance took their\nlife vests off and sank into the water."}]},{"cues":[{"time":367052,"text":"One man approached them\nwith a small baby perched on his shoulder,"},{"time":372999,"text":"nine months old -- Malek."},{"time":374673,"text":"He was holding onto a gas canister\nto stay afloat, and he said to them,"},{"time":379776,"text":"\"I fear I am not going to survive."},{"time":381750,"text":"I'm too weak. I don't have\nthe courage anymore.\""},{"time":384829,"text":"And he handed little Malek\nover to Bassem and to Doaa,"},{"time":389999,"text":"and they perched her onto the life ring."},{"time":393774,"text":"So now they were three,\nDoaa, Bassem and little Malek."}]},{"cues":[{"time":399212,"text":"And let me take a pause\nin this story right here"},{"time":402365,"text":"and ask the question:"},{"time":404687,"text":"why do refugees like Doaa\ntake these kinds of risks?"},{"time":411061,"text":"Millions of refugees are living\nin exile, in limbo."},{"time":417232,"text":"They're living in countries [fleeing]\nfrom a war that has been raging"},{"time":421556,"text":"for four years."},{"time":425634,"text":"Even if they wanted to return, they can't."},{"time":428819,"text":"Their homes, their businesses,"},{"time":431605,"text":"their towns and their cities\nhave been completely destroyed."},{"time":435151,"text":"This is a UNESCO World Heritage City,"},{"time":437999,"text":"Homs, in Syria."},{"time":441097,"text":"So people continue to flee\ninto neighboring countries,"},{"time":445686,"text":"and we build refugee camps\nfor them in the desert."},{"time":449309,"text":"Hundreds of thousands of people\nlive in camps like these,"},{"time":453343,"text":"and thousands and thousands more,\nmillions, live in towns and cities."},{"time":458340,"text":"And the communities,"},{"time":459582,"text":"the neighboring countries\nthat once welcomed them"},{"time":462462,"text":"with open arms and hearts"},{"time":464248,"text":"are overwhelmed."},{"time":466731,"text":"There are simply not enough schools,\nwater systems, sanitation."},{"time":471747,"text":"Even rich European countries\ncould never handle such an influx"},{"time":476394,"text":"without massive investment."},{"time":481407,"text":"The Syria war has driven almost\nfour million people over the borders,"},{"time":486457,"text":"but over seven million people\nare on the run inside the country."},{"time":491418,"text":"That means that over half\nthe Syrian population"},{"time":495133,"text":"has been forced to flee."},{"time":497766,"text":"Back to those neighboring\ncountries hosting so many."},{"time":503114,"text":"They feel that the richer world\nhas done too little to support them."},{"time":509401,"text":"And days have turned into months,\nmonths into years."},{"time":514483,"text":"A refugee's stay is supposed\nto be temporary."}]},{"cues":[{"time":518079,"text":"Back to Doaa and Bassem in the water."},{"time":521424,"text":"It was their second day,\nand Bassem was getting very weak."},{"time":526764,"text":"And now it was Doaa's turn\nto say to Bassem,"},{"time":530789,"text":"\"My love, please hold on to hope,\nto our future. We will make it.\""},{"time":537376,"text":"And he said to her,"},{"time":540081,"text":"\"I'm sorry, my love,\nthat I put you in this situation."},{"time":544542,"text":"I have never loved anyone\nas much as I love you.\""},{"time":550871,"text":"And he released himself into the water,"},{"time":554293,"text":"and Doaa watched as the love of her life\ndrowned before her eyes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":563888,"text":"Later that day,"},{"time":566328,"text":"a mother came up to Doaa with her\nsmall 18-month-old daughter, Masa."},{"time":572741,"text":"This was the little girl I showed you\nin the picture earlier,"},{"time":575690,"text":"with the life vests."},{"time":577562,"text":"Her older sister Sandra had just drowned,"},{"time":579779,"text":"and her mother knew she had to do\neverything in her power"},{"time":583922,"text":"to save her daughter."},{"time":585993,"text":"And she said to Doaa,\n\"Please take this child."},{"time":589874,"text":"Let her be part of you.\nI will not survive.\""},{"time":595125,"text":"And then she went away and drowned."}]},{"cues":[{"time":599825,"text":"So Doaa, the 19-year-old refugee\nwho was terrified of the water,"},{"time":604083,"text":"who couldn't swim,"},{"time":605999,"text":"found herself in charge\nof two little baby kids."},{"time":611615,"text":"And they were thirsty and they were hungry\nand they were agitated,"},{"time":615320,"text":"and she tried her best to amuse them,"},{"time":618042,"text":"to sing to them, to say words\nto them from the Quran."},{"time":623234,"text":"Around them, the bodies were bloating\nand turning black."},{"time":627692,"text":"The sun was blazing during the day."},{"time":629462,"text":"At night, there was a cold moon and fog."},{"time":632206,"text":"It was very frightening."},{"time":634976,"text":"On the fourth day in the water,\nthis is how Doaa probably looked"},{"time":639739,"text":"on the ring with her two children."}]},{"cues":[{"time":641884,"text":"A woman came on the fourth day\nand approached her"},{"time":645455,"text":"and asked her to take another child --"},{"time":648590,"text":"a little boy, just four years old."},{"time":652999,"text":"When Doaa took the little boy\nand the mother drowned,"},{"time":657040,"text":"she said to the sobbing child,"},{"time":659024,"text":"\"She just went away\nto find you water and food.\""},{"time":664388,"text":"But his heart soon stopped,"},{"time":666405,"text":"and Doaa had to release\nthe little boy into the water."}]},{"cues":[{"time":671023,"text":"Later that day,"},{"time":673072,"text":"she looked up into the sky with hope,"},{"time":676375,"text":"because she saw two planes\ncrossing in the sky."},{"time":680414,"text":"And she waved her arms,\nhoping they would see her,"},{"time":684937,"text":"but the planes were soon gone."}]},{"cues":[{"time":687317,"text":"But that afternoon,\nas the sun was going down,"},{"time":690244,"text":"she saw a boat, a merchant vessel."},{"time":694109,"text":"And she said, \"Please, God,\nlet them rescue me.\""},{"time":698150,"text":"She waved her arms and she felt\nlike she shouted for about two hours."},{"time":702134,"text":"And it had become dark,\nbut finally the searchlights found her"},{"time":706768,"text":"and they extended a rope,"},{"time":708999,"text":"astonished to see a woman\nclutching onto two babies."}]},{"cues":[{"time":714770,"text":"They pulled them onto the boat,\nthey got oxygen and blankets,"},{"time":718282,"text":"and a Greek helicopter came\nto pick them up"},{"time":721313,"text":"and take them to the island of Crete."}]},{"cues":[{"time":724353,"text":"But Doaa looked down and asked,\n\"What of Malek?\""},{"time":728400,"text":"And they told her the little baby\ndid not survive --"},{"time":731999,"text":"she drew her last breath\nin the boat's clinic."},{"time":736203,"text":"But Doaa was sure that as they had\nbeen pulled up onto the rescue boat,"},{"time":741999,"text":"that little baby girl had been smiling."}]},{"cues":[{"time":747278,"text":"Only 11 people survived\nthat wreck, of the 500."},{"time":754304,"text":"There was never an international\ninvestigation into what happened."},{"time":758999,"text":"There were some media reports\nabout mass murder at sea,"},{"time":763118,"text":"a terrible tragedy,"},{"time":764467,"text":"but that was only for one day."},{"time":767490,"text":"And then the news cycle moved on."}]},{"cues":[{"time":772536,"text":"Meanwhile, in a pediatric\nhospital on Crete,"},{"time":777102,"text":"little Masa was on the edge of death."},{"time":781681,"text":"She was really dehydrated.\nHer kidneys were failing."},{"time":785415,"text":"Her glucose levels were dangerously low."},{"time":787463,"text":"The doctors did everything\nin their medical power to save them,"},{"time":791053,"text":"and the Greek nurses never left her side,"},{"time":794737,"text":"holding her, hugging her,\nsinging her words."},{"time":796888,"text":"My colleagues also visited\nand said pretty words to her in Arabic."},{"time":802481,"text":"Amazingly, little Masa survived."}]},{"cues":[{"time":808192,"text":"And soon the Greek press started reporting\nabout the miracle baby,"},{"time":814152,"text":"who had survived four days in the water\nwithout food or anything to drink,"},{"time":819843,"text":"and offers to adopt her came\nfrom all over the country."}]},{"cues":[{"time":825466,"text":"And meanwhile, Doaa\nwas in another hospital on Crete,"},{"time":828880,"text":"thin, dehydrated."},{"time":831571,"text":"An Egyptian family took her into their\nhome as soon as she was released."},{"time":838248,"text":"And soon word went around\nabout Doaa's survival,"},{"time":843019,"text":"and a phone number\nwas published on Facebook."},{"time":847300,"text":"Messages started coming in."}]},{"cues":[{"time":850999,"text":"\"Doaa, do you know\nwhat happened to my brother?"},{"time":855811,"text":"My sister? My parents? My friends?\nDo you know if they survived?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":863201,"text":"One of those messages said,"},{"time":866999,"text":"\"I believe you saved\nmy little niece, Masa.\""},{"time":872249,"text":"And it had this photo."},{"time":875741,"text":"This was from Masa's uncle,"},{"time":878027,"text":"a Syrian refugee who had made it\nto Sweden with his family"},{"time":882773,"text":"and also Masa's older sister."},{"time":885647,"text":"Soon, we hope, Masa will be reunited\nwith him in Sweden,"},{"time":891355,"text":"and until then, she's being cared for\nin a beautiful orphanage in Athens."}]},{"cues":[{"time":898221,"text":"And Doaa? Well, word went around\nabout her survival, too."},{"time":904999,"text":"And the media wrote\nabout this slight woman,"},{"time":908736,"text":"and couldn't imagine how\nshe could survive all this time"},{"time":912672,"text":"under such conditions in that sea,"},{"time":915690,"text":"and still save another life."},{"time":920459,"text":"The Academy of Athens, one of Greece's\nmost prestigious institutions,"},{"time":925870,"text":"gave her an award of bravery,"},{"time":929250,"text":"and she deserves all that praise,"},{"time":932265,"text":"and she deserves a second chance."},{"time":935999,"text":"But she wants to still go to Sweden."},{"time":939463,"text":"She wants to reunite\nwith her family there."},{"time":941717,"text":"She wants to bring her mother\nand her father and her younger siblings"},{"time":945852,"text":"away from Egypt there as well,"},{"time":948194,"text":"and I believe she will succeed."},{"time":951399,"text":"She wants to become a lawyer\nor a politician"},{"time":954145,"text":"or something that can help\nfight injustice."},{"time":959063,"text":"She is an extraordinary survivor."}]},{"cues":[{"time":963215,"text":"But I have to ask:"},{"time":965803,"text":"what if she didn't have to take that risk?"},{"time":968099,"text":"Why did she have to go through all that?"},{"time":971226,"text":"Why wasn't there a legal way\nfor her to study in Europe?"},{"time":976314,"text":"Why couldn't Masa have taken\nan airplane to Sweden?"},{"time":980634,"text":"Why couldn't Bassem have found work?"},{"time":984125,"text":"Why is there no massive resettlement\nprogram for Syrian refugees,"},{"time":989571,"text":"the victims of the worst war of our times?"},{"time":993778,"text":"The world did this for the Vietnamese\nin the 1970s. Why not now?"},{"time":1000624,"text":"Why is there so little investment\nin the neighboring countries"},{"time":1005265,"text":"hosting so many refugees?"},{"time":1009113,"text":"And why, the root question,"},{"time":1011999,"text":"is so little being done to stop\nthe wars, the persecution"},{"time":1018419,"text":"and the poverty that is driving\nso many people"},{"time":1022999,"text":"to the shores of Europe?"},{"time":1025999,"text":"Until these issues are resolved,"},{"time":1028632,"text":"people will continue to take to the seas"},{"time":1031991,"text":"and to seek safety and asylum."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1036103,"text":"And what happens next?"},{"time":1038253,"text":"Well, that is largely Europe's choice."},{"time":1041108,"text":"And I understand the public fears."},{"time":1045005,"text":"People are worried about their security,\ntheir economies, the changes of culture."},{"time":1051893,"text":"But is that more important\nthan saving human lives?"},{"time":1056859,"text":"Because there is something\nfundamental here"},{"time":1059662,"text":"that I think overrides the rest,"},{"time":1062490,"text":"and it is about our common humanity."},{"time":1066719,"text":"No person fleeing war or persecution"},{"time":1071212,"text":"should have to die\ncrossing a sea to reach safety."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1076397,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1082753,"text":"One thing is for sure,"},{"time":1083944,"text":"that no refugee would be\non those dangerous boats"},{"time":1087151,"text":"if they could thrive where they are."},{"time":1089523,"text":"And no migrant would take\nthat dangerous journey"},{"time":1092825,"text":"if they had enough food\nfor themselves and their children."},{"time":1096735,"text":"And no one would put their life savings"},{"time":1099378,"text":"in the hands of those notorious smugglers"},{"time":1102195,"text":"if there was a legal way to migrate."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1105471,"text":"So on behalf of little Masa"},{"time":1109090,"text":"and on behalf of Doaa"},{"time":1111383,"text":"and of Bassem"},{"time":1113131,"text":"and of those 500 people\nwho drowned with them,"},{"time":1118292,"text":"can we make sure that they\ndid not die in vain?"},{"time":1122308,"text":"Could we be inspired by what happened,"},{"time":1125999,"text":"and take a stand for a world\nin which every life matters?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1132999,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1134334,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}